<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 01:53:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于对自己的区块链和立法的乐观情绪，Circle 激增</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-11/circle-s-first-quarter-revenue-increases-20-net-income-drops</link><description>由于人们对稳定币发行商 ARC 区块链项目的前景持乐观态度，并且美国立法者开始考虑一项具有里程碑意义的数字资产法案，Circle Internet Group Inc. 的股价上涨了 14%。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iHMGucUQHtCk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 10:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-11/circle-s-first-quarter-revenue-increases-20-net-income-drops</guid></item><item><title>参议员关注具有里程碑意义的数字资产法案，银行和加密货币支持者发生争执</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/banks-and-crypto-backers-tussle-as-senators-eye-stablecoin-bill</link><description>随着参议院一个重要小组开始考虑一项具有里程碑意义的数字资产法案，银行集团正在最后一刻对稳定币收益率进行妥协。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWhBANxj4P6o/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 23:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/banks-and-crypto-backers-tussle-as-senators-eye-stablecoin-bill</guid></item><item><title>DRW 支持的数字资产融资估值达 20 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-10/drw-backed-digital-asset-raising-money-at-2-billion-valuation</link><description>据知情人士透露，Digital Asset Holdings LLC 是多家大型银行和贸易公司使用的区块链背后的公司，正在从 a16z 加密货币等投资者那里筹集资金，估值约为 20 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itP.2DcQvYBo/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 11:37:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-10/drw-backed-digital-asset-raising-money-at-2-billion-valuation</guid></item></channel></rss>